Description
-----------

Select the width of the . [TGA](TGA_%28file_format%29 "TGA (file format)") frames generated with the [aviDemo](AviDemo_%28console_command%29 "AviDemo (console command)") command.

Usage
-----

At the console type...

    com_aviDemoWidth [int]

Parameters
----------

-   [int] - A positive value for the amount of horizontal pixels.

